The paper focuses on solving multi-robot planning problems, which falls under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA). The use of Dec-POMDPs and Dec-POSMDPs involves decision-making and planning, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of closed-loop belief space macro-actions, which involves control theory (cs.SY) and machine learning (cs.LG).
